{"1417930":{"success":true,"data":{"type":"game","name":"Lorn's Lure","steam_appid":1417930,"required_age":0,"is_free":false,"controller_support":"full","dlc":[4166680,2948850],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1417930/extras/f296cefef05518144331781438af6440.poster.avif?t=1766153079\" width=590 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1417930/extras/f296cefef05518144331781438af6440.webm?t=1766153079\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1417930/extras/f296cefef05518144331781438af6440.mp4?t=1766153079\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Lorn's Lure is an atmospheric narrative first-person platformer with novel climb-anything mechanics and modernized retro 3D graphics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leaving his home colony while tracking a mysterious glitch, an android finds himself in the midst of a vast and dangerous structure, completely hidden from his people's knowledge. Unable to go back, you must keep going to find out where he is being led... And why he left in the first place.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1417930/extras/a3483df80e9080c12626080e1e67cb3d.avif?t=1766153079\" width=600 height=70 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dark foreboding <strong>atmosphere</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Retro 90s PC graphics</strong>, with a modern flair.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover <strong>mysterious lore</strong> as you travel into the depths.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump, climb, slide, and scan your way around <strong>difficult challenges, using simple mechanics</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No &quot;Parkour Ledges&quot;. <strong>Climb almost any vertical wall face</strong> using your pickaxes!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's a tough game, and <strong>sometimes frustrating</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast and slow paced. <strong>Take in the sights</strong> as you traverse, and sometimes play as fast as a <strong>speed runner</strong>!</p></li></ul>","about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1417930/extras/f296cefef05518144331781438af6440.poster.avif?t=1766153079\" width=590 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1417930/extras/f296cefef05518144331781438af6440.webm?t=1766153079\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1417930/extras/f296cefef05518144331781438af6440.mp4?t=1766153079\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Lorn's Lure is an atmospheric narrative first-person platformer with novel climb-anything mechanics and modernized retro 3D graphics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leaving his home colony while tracking a mysterious glitch, an android finds himself in the midst of a vast and dangerous structure, completely hidden from his people's knowledge. Unable to go back, you must keep going to find out where he is being led... And why he left in the first place.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1417930/extras/a3483df80e9080c12626080e1e67cb3d.avif?t=1766153079\" width=600 height=70 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dark foreboding <strong>atmosphere</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Retro 90s PC graphics</strong>, with a modern flair.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover <strong>mysterious lore</strong> as you travel into the depths.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump, climb, slide, and scan your way around <strong>difficult challenges, using simple mechanics</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No &quot;Parkour Ledges&quot;. <strong>Climb almost any vertical wall face</strong> using your pickaxes!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's a tough game, and <strong>sometimes frustrating</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast and slow paced. <strong>Take in the sights</strong> as you traverse, and sometimes play as fast as a <strong>speed runner</strong>!</p></li></ul>","short_description":"An android is led through a vast structure by a glitch in his visual system. Lorn's Lure is an atmospheric narrative first-person platformer with novel climb-anything mechanics and modernized retro 3D graphics.","supported_languages":"English<strong>*</strong>, French, German, Spanish - Spain, Japanese, Korean, Polish, Portuguese - Brazil, Russian, Simplified Chinese, Turkish, Ukrainian<br><strong>*</strong>languages with full audio support","reviews":"“For anyone looking for a real challenge, there’s a lot to like. Speedrunners will have a lot of fun with it”<br>Alpha Beta Gamer<br><br>“It's weird, it's different, it's also strangely addictive”<br>Vinesauce Vinny<br>","header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1417930/header.jpg?t=1766153079","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1417930/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1766153079","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1417930/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1766153079","website":"https://rubeki.com/","pc_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class